of confined to this desk.

177
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:39,122
- Do you ship?
- Special delivery.

178
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:41,328
You could have it
in two or three days.

179
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:43,050
They'd even assemble it
for you.

180
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:44,486
Well,

181
00:11:44,680 --> 00:11:45,966
