WOMAN:
You look absolutely divine!

215
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,720
Turn around.

216
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,211
- Please.
- Come on.

217
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,010
- Perfect, wonderful shoulders.
- (thumps)

218
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,326
