with me to Europe.

263
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:56,761
- Women!
- You said it, pal.

264
00:14:56,920 --> 00:14:58,524
- I don't believe it!
- Oh, look who's coming.

265
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:00,682
Does the House
Un-American Activities know

266
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:02,604
- you two are back on the streets?
